name: Celebration
description:
About This Piece
A celebration after the final match on the high school football championship in my city.

About "Before Pandemic" Collection
Before Pandemic is a limited edition NFTs collection based on images that I captured before the pandemic started. There's a lot of things that seem to be strange these days but are pretty normal before the pandemic. Remembering all those memories while hoping someday that will come again soon.
There are 3 images in this collection and all of them are captured on 35mm film. Each image comes in 10 editions only. Comes in 3000*2000px png container. Grab yours only for 1 tez.
